Debugging node - CMDLINE
===============================
debug> - gets inited
node inspect <file.js>
n -  next statement
c - continue

--- repl  mode: Switches between debug and watch mode.
> person : shows the person object, like the watch window

get and set values.
>person.age = 100
>person.age + 100

